es/1.2/VRzBJCRNS4_hOx6_n6Nmpg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD04MjcuNDgyNQ--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/q0q6MY5YX_EKyag8EMTFZA--~B/aD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/507824642a3f22e31d7b755a8f51d104\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVRzBJCRNS4_hOx6_n6Nmpg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD04MjcuNDgyNQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fq0q6MY5YX_EKyag8EMTFZA--~B%2FaD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2F507824642a3f22e31d7b755a8f51d104&h=d18d60f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲網友近日發現AirPods的一個大秘密。（示意圖／取自unsplash）<br />\n<br />\n藍牙耳機近幾年興起，不少人在選購手機時，也會順便購入一組，方便聆聽音樂、通話使用，其中備受討論的就是蘋果的AirPods，不過，近日就有網友分享「AirPods此生最大的秘密」貼文引爆熱議。<br />\n<br />\n一名網友在IG限時動態貼文指出「<span class=\"red\">看到國外的抖音影片，有人說AirPods盒子底部拉開有送一條線？我覺得不太可能，想說怎麼可能大家那麼笨，竟然不知道底下有一條線？但我還是決定去看一下，我買了兩年丟在櫃子沒動的AirPods盒，結果打開真的有！超傻眼的」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IkZhCtbaFBiqzKQeCmn8aw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/f99e75abac31800ca4f337c13ea9ca24\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIkZhCtbaFBiqzKQeCmn8aw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2Ff99e75abac31800ca4f337c13ea9ca24&h=5fd3d8a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲網友發現AirPods盒子底部拿起來有送原廠線。（圖／李先生授權提供）<br />\n<br />\n貼文一出，網友紛紛挖出自己的AirPods盒子打開，結果紛紛驚呼<span class=\"red\">「天阿！我也是第一次知道」、「欸結果我也真的是這麼笨，底部真的有送線」、「買了兩個禮拜我才發現」、「我已經把盒子丟掉了.....」、「謝謝你這則......＝＝」、「去年收到的聖誕禮物，看到你這則才去挖盒子...找到了」、「真的超傻眼....竟然真的有送線」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n而《NOWnews》記者也訪問到發這則限時動態的李先生，他表示，因為朋友告訴他看到國外抖音影片，有人做這個開箱，他不相信真有此事，於是挖出自己買了兩年的AirPods盒子，打開底部，一條原廠蘋果充電線就繞在底部，讓他直呼「真的是AirPods最驚人的秘密」。（編輯：張嘉哲）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DwxM5bj9kN3GXYCVa0oPFA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/9161c4199cc89eba10dbe1a36b373d4f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDwxM5bj9kN3GXYCVa0oPFA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2F9161c4199cc89eba10dbe1a36b373d4f&h=1731bdbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲而記者也實際拿出自己的AirPods盒子，打開底部真的有一條蘋果原廠線，買兩個月從未發現。（圖／記者張嘉哲攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/5155316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F5155316&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=212dddea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/5155316</a><br />\n點會咁都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買完搖下個盒都聽到聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要有d人扔埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得apple開始cut配件賺多你班水魚一筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"我唔知  盒都掉埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527413f7363565b41a79bf151b3778a77fcec21d","tid":2353954,"uid":26602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90e6a91669dfcbd26dff93b32fce823f88cd655e","tid":2353954,"uid":178875,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"b0fb0d465fca8a7c6d57e2d641800cd68b3b6ffc","tid":2353954,"uid":374134,"like":4,"dislike":30,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0USTrV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0USTrV.png&h=48f470db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:33:37.000Z","msg":"原來真係有咁多傻人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />